{"books":[{"id":"whb","name":"文汇报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"title":"德诗选译四首","authors":["A·卜拿吞","G·A比尔格","W·伏格维德","刘盛亚","席勒"],"dates":[{"year":1956,"month":11,"day":30}],"is_range_date":false,"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"刘盛亚"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"权杖"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"W·伏格维德"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"檥杖，你说吧，谁把你送给教皇"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用来统治德意志全邦?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他经常使用狡计，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"弄得天地无光。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他宣讲每个信徒没有把利息付清，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"国内是罪恶飞扬。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我想，天堂里金银有什么用处，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"珍宝将使圣徒有所损伤。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"檥杖啊，你蒙上了耻辱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在德国无知的男女才把你信仰。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"作者W.Vogelweid。(1170——1230)，其祖先是奥地利人。他当时反对教皇，诗名很盛。原作是古德文，现在是根据新德文译出来的。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"农民给暴君的诗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"G·A比尔格"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"公爵，你是谁啊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毫无顾忌地用车轮和"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大马践踏我?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"公爵，你是谁啊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的从人，你的猎狗残害我，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"难道不永远留在我心中么?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你是谁啊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不管是播种或是寒冷的时候，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"野兽般摧毁我的粮食?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"禾苗被你出猎时损坏，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"粮食被你的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"狗、马吃完。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你，公爵啊，一滴汗不流，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不拿耙也不把犁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可是粮食是我工作的收获!——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你把上帝放在哪儿呀?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上帝咒骂你是抢夺!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"暴君呀，你将永堕地狱!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"作者Gottfried August Buergor(1747——1794)"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新世纪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"席勒"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"崇高底目的必定有成就，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"真理的闪电好像龙游，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就是鬼魂也将得救。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"认识自由，本身就要争斗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不分人种，也不分时间的长久。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"复仇的人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"A·卜拿吞"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把每一支奴隶的军队"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都摧毁并化作飞灰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可是，薄木的棺材上面，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都有新的花朵在开。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们最后的力量消灭时，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"才满意地进入坟墓，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而我们的骨骼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却要像一个复仇的人般复活。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"Augustvo nPlaten(1796——835)浪漫主义作家，这是他著名的一首政治诗。"}],"comments":[],"origin":"","comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":1,"page_end":1,"alias":""},"tags":[{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}